item.title: Market and Enrolment Analysis of Equity Students in Victoria
item.description: As an intern at the University of Melbourne, used my data science skills to help realize the university’s objectives in student access and equity, and improved diversity in the student cohort. They wished to engage and win students of various backgrounds, including, but not limited to, Low Social-Economic student, First Nation students, and Disavantaged Background students. I was part of a 3-person diverse team, and we examined the VTAC Masterfile dataset that comprised of more than 360 attributes.
